{"tid":918813,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[詢眾要求重開] GFRIEND YUJU 透過VLIVE公開近況\"想你了\"","createTime":"2018-11-27T13:48:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T08:11:56.000Z","uid":74065,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8fd7d592a148f740634a4e22cfc176169bc21bd8","tid":918813,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T13:48:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/http://photo.jtbc.joins.com/news/2018/11/27/20181127192012356.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fphoto.jtbc.joins.com%2Fnews%2F2018%2F11%2F27%2F20181127192012356.jpg&h=57c736c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n組合GFRIEND的YUJU透過VLIVE公開了自己的近況.<br />\n<br />\nYUJU 27日突然出現在所願和信飛的NAVER V現場並露出臉龐說:&quot;我想看到Buddy(粉絲名).&quot;<br />\n<br />\n距離上個月27日最後一次參加正式活動僅過了一個月YUJU以健康開朗的樣子消除了粉絲們的憂慮.<br />\n<br />\nYUJU沒有參加行程，而是通過其他成員重新錄下有主部分的音源登上舞臺很多人對YUJU的近況感到好奇<br />\n<br />\n對此,經紀公司表示:&quot;計劃從12月開始正常參與活動.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n你班ONCE咁高興人地失蹤阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22798545faa83e06a2bbfe3c1c0e01a65feee1b7","tid":918813,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T13:49:33.000Z","msg":"有無變到樣"},{"pid":"0d3e8685bd459af22bf7d0dd5d1f54261fa241ef","tid":918813,"uid":213300,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T13:50:21.000Z","msg":"真係冇乜點變"},{"pid":"b54bbdc5ada67876142e5d983e06ff0a34d6eb48","tid":918813,"uid":74065,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T13:51:39.000Z","msg":"睇黎真係用左一個月作正規專D歌<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又RV又MAMAMOO又GF<br />\n我不行了"},{"pid":"006697ef96fcb48ecf6e67d46099020520cad3d4","tid":918813,"uid":91227,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T13:51:45.000Z","msg":"仲索左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f821b97bc0a4a3f64668eeae401060befe174599","tid":918813,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"006697ef96fcb48ecf6e67d46099020520cad3d4","tid":918813,"uid":91227,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T13:51:45.000Z","msg":"仲索左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T13:59:30.000Z","msg":"誇張左"},{"pid":"c3539bdde73895902036b57e14162c0c4619a9ef","tid":918813,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T14:01:45.000Z","msg":"南韓女團GFRIEND因清新可愛的風格，以及「刀群舞」的堅強舞蹈實力，深受許多粉絲喜愛。行程滿檔的她們，成員Yuju卻缺席了整個11月的行程，神隱1個月，公司甚至為此發出聲明，終於在27日與成員一起現身，才讓歌迷放心不少，感動直呼「妳終於出現了」。<br />\n<br />\nYuju無預警缺席團體活動，令歌迷一頭霧水，神隱將近1個月，她27日現身GFRIEND直播裡，與信飛、所願現身向粉絲介紹「宿舍新成員」，她抱著其中一隻狗狗，並主動走進鏡頭里向粉絲打招呼，雖是素顏但氣色看起來不錯，邊看著留言邊回應：「我的Buddy，我的愛。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3724/d3724679.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3724%2Fd3724679.jpg&h=e0cbc8e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Yuju神隱一個月素顏現身。（圖／翻攝自Vlive）<br />\n<br />\n由於直播無預警開啟，Yuju、信飛、所願3人幾乎都是素顏狀態，只開了19分鐘便決定關掉鏡頭，她們害羞笑說：「我們太快關掉，絕對不是太丟臉才關掉，下次更美一點時再開，大家掰掰。」而Yuju親自報平安現身，也讓許多歌迷感動表示「看到臉就好了」、「好想你」。"},{"pid":"dc783c3bc5c65bdeb058ff66eae20cdbb3fe5a4e","tid":918813,"uid":52073,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T14:05:10.000Z","msg":"我射精gfd"},{"pid":"133c715551c2c0371cfeec8b7be3eae39155d9e0","tid":918813,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc783c3bc5c65bdeb058ff66eae20cdbb3fe5a4e","tid":918813,"uid":52073,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T14:05:10.000Z","msg":"我射精gfd"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T14:08:06.000Z","m